00:13:26,631 --> 00:13:29,895
[laughs]

273
00:13:29,939 --> 00:13:31,941
<i>♪ </i>

274
00:13:31,984 --> 00:13:35,118
[gurgling]

275
00:13:35,161 --> 00:13:36,771
Here you go.

276
00:13:36,815 --> 00:13:39,687
- That's 1,000 bucks.
