277
00:13:42,647 --> 00:13:43,996
Ahh.

278
00:13:47,086 --> 00:13:48,871
I just love that color.

279
00:13:48,914 --> 00:13:50,698
- Yeah, it matches
your lip gloss.

280
00:13:53,223 --> 00:13:56,095
[starts engine]

281
00:13:56,139 --> 00:13:57,923
What's that?

