00:13:57,967 --> 00:13:59,142
It's a hobby.

283
00:13:59,185 --> 00:14:06,062
<i>♪ </i>

284
00:14:20,163 --> 00:14:23,731
[crying]

285
00:14:23,775 --> 00:14:26,691
<i>[somber music]</i>

286
00:14:26,734 --> 00:14:33,654
<i>♪ </i>

287
00:14:36,005 --> 00:14:38,181
I'm gonna call him in.

288
00:14:40,009 --> 00:14:42,620
Are you ready?

289
00:14:42,663 --> 00:14:44,578
- I don't know how anybody
could be ready for this.

290
00:14:45,710 --> 00:14:47,016
I know.

291
00:14:57,374 --> 00:14:59,724
Junior.

292
00:14:59,767 --> 00:15:01,813
Can you come in here
