783
00:45:42,391 --> 00:45:44,785
I got you now, bitch!

784
00:45:47,396 --> 00:45:50,094
But I'll let you go
on one condition.

785
00:45:51,139 --> 00:45:53,794
[panting]

786
00:45:53,837 --> 00:45:55,796
What?

787
00:45:57,972 --> 00:46:01,323
- All you gotta do
is kill Jake.

788
00:46:06,807 --> 00:46:08,939
Everybody's gotta die sometime,
so--

789
00:46:08,983 --> 00:46:10,158
That's true.

790
00:46:10,201 --> 00:46:12,900
- I mean, I've died myself
many times,

791
00:46:12,943 --> 00:46:14,379
so it's no big deal.

792
00:46:18,122 --> 00:46:23,084
- You want me to kill Jake?
Why?

793
00:46:23,127 --> 00:46:26,304
- Don't tell me you've
never thought about it.

794
00:46:26,348 --> 00:46:28,829
You get off on hurting Jake.

795
00:46:33,137 --> 00:46:34,095
Yeah.

796
00:46:37,185 --> 00:46:39,970
Okay, fine, I'll admit it.

797
00:46:40,014 --> 00:46:41,189
I have thought about it.

798
00:46:43,104 --> 00:46:45,846
You're right.

799
00:46:45,889 --> 00:46:48,239
I do wanna kill Jake.

800
00:46:48,283 --> 00:46:49,327
I knew it.

801
00:46:50,938 --> 00:46:52,853
You wanna know I'd do it?

802
00:46:52,896 --> 00:46:54,332
Duh!

803
00:46:56,073 --> 00:46:58,206
I'm all ears.
[beeping]

804
00:46:58,249 --> 00:46:59,772
Okay.

805
00:47:03,776 --> 00:47:05,213
I'd beat him to death...

806
00:47:08,042 --> 00:47:09,478
with this.

807
00:47:11,219 --> 00:47:12,829
Can I watch?

808
00:47:12,873 --> 00:47:13,874
[floorboard creaks]

809
00:47:13,917 --> 00:47:16,050
Aha!

810
00:47:16,093 --> 00:47:18,835
Do it, Lexy!
Kill him!

811
00:47:18,879 --> 00:47:19,923
Damn it!

812
00:47:19,967 --> 00:47:21,272
- Ha ha!
- Ahh!

813
00:47:21,316 --> 00:47:23,448
- [Tazer crackling]
- No! [screams]

814
00:47:23,492 --> 00:47:24,449
Jake!

815
00:47:24,493 --> 00:47:25,929
<i>♪ </i>

816
00:47:25,973 --> 00:47:27,365
Shit!

817
00:47:27,409 --> 00:47:28,932
- [beeping]
- Come on, come on, come on!

818
00:47:28,976 --> 00:47:30,542
<i>♪ </i>

819
00:47:30,586 --> 00:47:33,371
[groans]

820
00:47:33,415 --> 00:47:35,983
I'm too old for this shit.

821
00:47:43,468 --> 00:47:46,428
[laughs]

822
00:47:48,909 --> 00:47:50,301
[beeping]

823
00:47:50,345 --> 00:47:52,825
- Guys.
He's headed back downstairs.

824
00:47:52,869 --> 00:47:53,914
- Okay.
[grunting]

825
00:47:56,220 --> 00:47:57,874
- He didn't even try
to kill me.

826
00:47:57,918 --> 00:47:59,223
- Me neither.
- What the hell?

827
00:47:59,267 --> 00:48:02,923
- Hello?
<i>[police radio chatter]</i>

828
00:48:02,966 --> 00:48:05,012
Devon, are you here?

829
00:48:05,055 --> 00:48:06,578
Mom?

830
00:48:06,622 --> 00:48:08,058
Ahh!

831
00:48:08,102 --> 00:48:10,234
Hey, Devon, watch this!

832
00:48:10,278 --> 00:48:11,583
[screams]

833
00:48:11,627 --> 00:48:13,455
Mom! Mom!

834
00:48:13,498 --> 00:48:15,239
[screaming]

835
00:48:15,283 --> 00:48:17,415
- Whoa! [laughs]
Ahh!

836
00:48:18,329 --> 00:48:20,027
[screaming]

837
00:48:20,070 --> 00:48:21,550
Mom!

838
00:48:23,334 --> 00:48:25,423
[bones cracking]

839
00:48:25,467 --> 00:48:30,080
[Chucky laughs]

840
00:48:30,124 --> 00:48:37,000
<i>♪ </i>

841
00:48:43,267 --> 00:48:50,187
<i>♪ </i>

842
00:48:59,153 --> 00:49:06,073
<i>♪ </i>

